], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}, {\"begin\": 175, \"end\": 179, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.999773728465551, \"rank\": 0.0001272016581506638, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 195, \"end\": 212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999998893622494, \"rank\": 1.1062555644585679e-07, \"text\": \"Sydney university\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Sydney\"}, {\"begin\": 302, \"end\": 307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999978470103073, \"rank\": 2.1529943662068104e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn thanked her supporters and said she was glad to bring them some joy, in a video from a Brussels street posted on her Instagram account on Thursday.\", \"from\": 375, \"to\": 527, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 375, \"end\": 379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.999773728465551, \"rank\": 0.0001272016581506638, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 467, \"end\": 475, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brussels\", \"score\": 0.999984894444145, \"rank\": 1.1991712350924215e-05, \"text\": \"Brussels\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brussels\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brussels\"}, {\"begin\": 497, \"end\": 506, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.763454042045135e-26, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did not realise that that would also open the door to so much hate, which has frankly been pretty devastating,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 529, \"to\": 653, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Well, I went out there and I had fun.\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 693, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did take it very seriously.\", \"from\": 694, \"to\": 723, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I worked my butt off preparing for the Olympics and I gave my all.\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 790, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Truly.\\\"\", \"from\": 791, \"to\": 798, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn's kangaroo-mimicking moves and Australia-logoed tracksuit have been parodied worldwide, including by late-night US television host Jimmy Fallon.\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 949, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 800, \"end\": 804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.999773728465551, \"rank\": 0.0001272016581506638, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 917, \"end\": 919, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9917410188225927, \"rank\": 0.006197319523371135, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 936, \"end\": 948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Fallon\", \"score\": 0.9999998750943255, \"rank\": 1.2490573696029733e-07, \"text\": \"Jimmy Fallon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Fallon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Fallon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has faced much stronger criticism and ridicule online.\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 1009, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Australian Olympic Committee has decried a \\\"misleading and bullying\\\" online petition that described Gunn's performance as \\\"unethical\\\" and questioned how she was chosen for Paris.\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1193, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1011, \"end\": 1025, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.536120497516052e-25, \"text\": \"The Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\"}, {\"begin\": 1015, \"end\": 1043, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Australian Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1115, \"end\": 1119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.999773728465551, \"rank\": 0.0001272016581506638, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 1187, \"end\": 1192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999978470103073, \"rank\": 2.1529943662068104e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In regards to the allegations and misinformation floating around, I'd like to ask everyone to please refer to the recent statement made by the AOC,\\\" Gunn said in her video.\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1368, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1339, \"end\": 1342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.5642758308390284, \"rank\": 0.772182937548897, \"text\": \"AOC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1345, \"end\": 1349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.999773728465551, \"rank\": 0.0001272016581506638, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The poll on Change.org, which garnered tens of thousands of signatures demanding a public apology from the dancer, was unavailable on the platform on Friday.\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1527, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1382, \"end\": 1392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Change.org\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Change.org\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Change.org\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Change.org\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn said she planned to remain in Europe for a few weeks for some \\\"pre-planned downtime\\\".\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1619, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1529, \"end\": 1533, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.999773728465551, \"rank\": 0.0001272016581506638, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the meantime, she asked the media to \\\"stop harassing\\\" her family, friends and the breakdancing community.\", \"from\": 1621, \"to\": 1729, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everyone has been through a lot as a result of this so I ask you to please respect their privacy,\\\" she said, promising to answer more questions on her return to Australia.\", \"from\": 1731, \"to\": 1903, \"entities\": [{\